body:
`moreLikeThis` has the following syntax:

```javascript
 {
   "$search": {
     "index": index name, // optional, defaults to "default"
     "moreLikeThis": {
       "like": [
         {
           <"field-name">: <"field-value">,
           ...
         },
         ...
       ],
       "score": <options>
     }
   }
 }
```
